query: SELECT Id, WorkOrderId, ParentWorkOrderLineItemId, RootWorkOrderLineItemId, Product2.External_Id__c, Order.migrationid__c, Description, StartDate, EndDate, Status, PricebookEntry.External_Id__c, Quantity, UnitPrice, Discount, Duration, DurationType, WorkType.External_Id__c, Street, City, State, PostalCode, Country, StateCode, CountryCode, Latitude, Longitude, GeocodeAccuracy, ServiceTerritory.migrationid__c, Subject, Priority, Location.Name, MinimumCrewSize, RecommendedCrewSize, ServiceReportTemplate.MasterLabel, SuggestedMaintenanceDate, FSL__IsFillInCandidate__c, FSL__VisitingHours__r.External_Id__c, Delivery_Date__c, Frequency__c, Part_Description__c, Part_Number__c, Product_Status__c, Quantity__c, WS_Legacy_ID__c, migrationid__c, Resolution_Summary__c, Root_Cause__c FROM WorkOrderLineItem WHERE WorkOrder.Revenue_Branch__r.name IN ('Cherry Hill','Houston East','Los Angeles') AND WorkOrder.StartDate >= LAST_N_MONTHS:2 AND WorkOrder.EndDate <= NEXT_N_MONTHS:2
